          "description": "<ul><li><p>Led deprecation of a legacy customer push notification service and migration to a modern Spring Boot application, simplifying architecture and reducing infrastructure costs by <strong>~$1,800/month</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Retired a dedicated marketing-events Lambda and consolidated delivery-partner marketing events into a central event-processing service, improving metrics across <strong>40+ event types</strong> from <strong>5</strong> upstream systems at <strong>575K events/min</strong> while cutting cloud spend by <strong>$400/month</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Deprecated a legacy EC2-based vendor identity resolution service by simplifying Kafka topic architecture and reducing cross-service hops, reliably handling <strong>3.8M requests/day</strong> and saving <strong>$300/month</strong> in infrastructure costs.</p></li><li><p>Integrated WhatsApp OTP for international user login flows via an internal gRPC service for secure mobile number resolution, enabling logins for <strong>12,500 international users/day (~1,600 iOPD)</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Built catalog integration between a quick-commerce storefront and a paid social ads partner, enabling near–real-time catalog sync for <strong>2M updates/day</strong> across <strong>13M items</strong> and reducing product-detail-page miss rate from <strong>10% to 0% </strong>effective increase of <strong>20,000 iOPD</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Drove marketing-events and push-notification multi-tenancy for new consumer and partner applications, supporting <strong>450K daily marketing events</strong> and <strong>650K daily push notifications</strong> for new business verticals.</p></li><li><p>Developed an LLM-powered reliability and cost-report generator integrating Opsgenie, Slack, Grafana, and AWS Cost Explorer, reducing weekly on-call report preparation time from <strong>4–5 hours</strong> to <strong>minutes</strong>.</p></li></ul><p></p>",
